metadata.name: Crayona's Home-Studio
metadata.description:
I have discovered this section from the heart of this sentence:

"Mainly I just want a huge desk, enough to have computer plus tons of papers spread out.  Like to be able to have more than one project out without having to clean up another one.
I’m also into the idea that the best workspaces becomes an extension of your body and way you think.  There’s a wonderful tweet about this I couldn’t find it,  if anyone has it bookmarked please share!
(but I’ve never really mastered that part)"

2048*2048 pxl
